# <Incident/Procedure Title>

**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD
**System(s) affected:** 
**Severity:** (data loss / downtime / degraded / none — near miss)

## Symptoms
What was actually observed. Exact error messages, what looked wrong first.

## Root Cause
What was actually true, once found. Not "what we suspected" — the real cause.

## Investigation Path (optional but valuable)
How you got from symptom to cause. This is the part that saves time next incident.

## Recovery Steps
What was actually done, in order, to fix it. Commands if relevant.

## Prevention / Follow-up
Concrete changes made or still needed. Link to procedures/ or Ansible commit if applicable.
